---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const canonicalUrl = `${new URL(Astro.request.url).origin}/returnRefundPolicy`;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund & Return Policy"
  canonical={canonicalUrl}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script is:inline>
      if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
          if (typeof window.gtag === 'function') {
            window.gtag('config', 'G-NQ94Z6HWGV', {
              page_path: '/returnRefundPolicy'
            });
            window.gtag('config', 'AW-17641771829', {
              page_path: '/returnRefundPolicy'
            });
          }
        });
      }
    </script>
  </Fragment>
  <section class="py-20 px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-white tracking-[1.2px]">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-cyber text-primary mb-10 text-center">Refund & Return Policy</h1>

    <h2 class='text-3xl font-cyber text-secondary text-center'>Overview</h2>

    <p class="mb-6 text-md font-sans font-bold text-accent">
        Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If 30 days have passed since your purchase, we can’t offer you a full refund or exchange.
        To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.
        Several types of goods are exempt from being returned. ALL CORES PURCHASED ARE NOT ABLE TO BE RETURNED
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-cyber text-primary mt-10 mb-2">Refunds</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-sans">
      Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund. If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-cyber text-primary mt-10 mb-2">Refundable Items</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-sans">
      Only items that are unused and in their original packaging are eligible for a refund. This includes all parts and accessories that were not installed or used. <span class="font-bold">Only regular priced items may be refunded. Sale items cannot be refunded.</span>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-cyber text-primary mt-10 mb-2">Late or missing refunds FOR RETURNED CORES</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-sans">
      If you haven’t received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.
      Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.
      Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund is posted.
    </p>

    <p class='mb-4 font-bold font-sans'>If you’ve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fasmotorsports.com" class="text-accent hover:text-white">support@fasmotorsports.com</a> immediately.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-cyber text-primary mt-10 mb-2">Exchanges</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. If you need to exchange it for the same item, send us an email at <a href="mailto:support@fasmotorsports.com" class="text-accent hover:text-white">support@fasmotorsports.com</a> and send your item to <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=6161+Riverside+Dr,+Punta+Gorda,+FL+33982" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"  class="text-accent hover:text-white">
        6161 Riverside Dr. Punta Gorda, FL 33982</a>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-cyber text-primary mt-10 mb-2">Shipping Returns</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      To return your product, you should ship your product to
      <a
        href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&amp;destination=6161+Riverside+Dr,+Punta+Gorda,+FL+33982"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-accent hover:text-white"
      >
        6161 Riverside Dr. Punta Gorda, FL 33982
      </a>.
      You will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable. Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged product to reach you may vary.
      <span class="font-bold">If you are returning more expensive items, you may consider using a trackable shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We don’t guarantee that we will receive your returned item.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions, please contact us at
      <a href="mailto:support@fasmotorsports.com" class="text-accent hover:text-white">support@fasmotorsports.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
